{
  "stem": "14613.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But somehow, we were able to change the names or the numbers with some other friends who also were supposed to be separated, so that we went together and the other brothers or father and son went together.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we were on this march here at night, being on this hillside, and we had a little food, which we got from the camp before we departed, my brother would tie me into a tree and the food, so that I wouldn't roll down.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would sleep next to me so nobody would steal the food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it worked OK for a few nights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think the third night, somebody somehow-- and we were dead tired, you have to realize, you know-- somebody cut the rope, and I ended somewhere completely different with no food.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were talking to ourself now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's bad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we're already out of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you have to realize that the march was not an easy march.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what was happening to the people that could not march, they fell down on the roadside and the Germans shot them, so that throughout the night, all we could hear, tra-ta-ta, tra-ta-ta.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because whoever dropped was shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And thousands of people were shot every, every night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened the fourth day, as we marched-- as we stayed surrounded in the, in the forest, they suddenly called us in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they say, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started to march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that point, as I say, we didn't have any food, and we felt already lousy after all this walking.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we felt we cannot march much longer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were falling slowly, slowly towards the end of the columns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And here, what happened is suddenly very unusual.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
